# AI features (summaries + article Q&A) — any OpenAI-compatible endpoint works:
# OpenAI itself, vLLM, LiteLLM, Ollama (http://localhost:11434/v1), etc.
# Copy to .env and fill in. Without these, NewsRead runs fine as a plain reader.
OPENAI_BASE_URL=https://api.openai.com/v1
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini

# Web search + page extraction for the Q&A agent (https://tavily.com, free tier).
# Optional: without it the assistant answers from the article text only.
TAVILY_API_KEY=tvly-...
